The Plugsky OS CLI installer downloads and embeds the opencode binary
(an AI coding agent) as a private runtime at `~/.plugsky/.runtime/`. The
upstream binary is unmodified; the user-facing "plugsky" command is a thin
shim that rebrands --version and --help output and pre-loads the Plugsky
provider configuration.

